<L>__{interior circus control's office night}
<A>__{control sits surrounded by files. a dim green lamp on his desk the only illumination. he looks ill, tense with waiting. cigarette stubs piled in the ashtray. he listens to the solitary phone below him in the building. then it is joined by a second. then a third... control listens, nerves stretched to their limit. from just outside the sound of someone running up the wooden staircase. a knock.}
